ion%3A+A+History&amp;rft.pages=152&amp;rft.pub=McFarland&amp;rft.date=2010&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-7864-4409-0&amp;rft.au=Michael+C.+Thomsett&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOld+Christian\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Michael Brenner; Jeremiah Riemer (2010). <i>A Short History of the Jews</i>. Princeton University Press. p.&#160;122. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-691-14351-4\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-691-14351-4\">978-0-691-14351-4</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+Short+History+of+the+Jews&amp;rft.pages=122&amp;rft.pub=Princeton+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2010&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-691-14351-4&amp;rft.au=Michael+Brenner&amp;rft.au=Jeremiah+Riemer&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOld+Christian\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bibliography\">Bibliography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Old_Christian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Bibliography\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><cite class=\"citation book\">J. L\u00facio de Azevedo (1989). <i>Hist\u00f3ria dos Crist\u00e3os Novos Portugueses</i>. Lisboa: Cl\u00e1ssica Editora.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Hist%C3%B3ria+dos+Crist%C3%A3os+Novos+Portugueses&amp;rft.place=Lisboa&amp;rft.pub=Cl%C3%A1ssica+Editora&amp;rft.d